{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Produits{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
  <div class="container">

    <div class="card mt-5">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="{{ asset('/images/image.jpg') }}" alt="Card image cap">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">{{produit.name}}</h5>
        <p class="card-text mt-4">{{produit.description}}</p>
        <p class="card-text mt-4 lead text-justify">

          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Aut ipsam possimus aut distinctio eligendi qui reprehenderit libero ea dicta nihil? Aut fugiat omnis hic vitae quis aut possimus rerum est reprehenderit voluptatem. Eos optio galisum non obcaecati laudantium qui debitis autem ut eius quod qui fugit similique quo sequi nisi. Quo cupiditate eius ea obcaecati harum a sunt earum qui repudiandae quam ut fuga galisum. Vel ullam quod nam soluta veniam eum saepe animi sit culpa quod quisquam molestiae. Hic optio consequatur eos quae tempore et officiis illo sed dolor laborum ea blanditiis rerum.

        </p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">

          <div >
            <p class="mt-5 ">
              <i class="fas fa-check text-success me-3"></i>
              Reprise gratuite de votre ancien produit</p>
            <p>
              <i class="fas fa-home  text-danger me-3"></i>
              Livraison internationale en 3 jours ouvrés</p>
            <p>
              <i class="fas fa-truck  text-danger me-3"></i>
              Livré en point retrait dès demain
            </p>
            <p>
              <i class="fas fa-flag-usa  text-danger me-3"></i>
              Expédié depuis nos entrepôts régionaux américain</p>
          </div>

          <div class=" card mt-5  fw-bold text-success h3 w-25 p-3 ">
            <span>
              {{produit.price}}
              &euro;
              <i class="fas fa-credit-card ms-5 text-secondary "></i>
            </span>

            <span class="text-dark h6  mt-5">
              Quantité :
              <select class="form-select w-25 ms-5 me-n5" aria-label="Default select example">
                <option value="1">1</option>
                <option value="2">2</option>
                <option value="3">3</option>
              </select>
            </span>

            <button class="btn btn-outline-success mt-2">
              <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i>
              Ajouter au panier</button>

          </div>

        </div>
        <p class="card-text mb-5 mt-4">
          <small class=" text-success fst-italic fw-bold mt-5">
            Il reste
            {{produit.stock}}
            en stock</small>
        </p>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <button class="btn btn-warning  me-2">
            <i class="fas fa-heart text-white"></i>
          </button>

          <button class="btn btn-outline-dark">
            <i class="fas fa-pencil"></i>
            Modifier
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

{% endblock %}
